data.text:
Changodar, Gujarat, India

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 22.918116, 72.440613.

Changodar (ચાંગોદર) is a small town located in the neighborhood of Ahmedabad, the most populous city in the state of Gujarat. It is situated about 20 kilometers southwest of the city center. It is a purely residential area, with a number of hotels and shopping malls. Despite its quite far away location, it is not difficult to reach the town by using the highway. Gulmohar Greens Golf & Country Club Limited is located 8 kilometers north of the town.
